data.name: SqlSelectCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT RecordID, Username, Engineer, Stress, LiaisonEngineer, Operations, ID, Location, Admin, LeadEngineer, Active, Email, QAManager, ProductionManager, ProgramManager, DAO, Design, QC, NewNCR, CloseNCR, SuperUser FROM tblUsers

data.name: SqlInsertCommand1.CommandText
